<i>... and at the end of the maze he makes
the drop. He's done it 7 times so far.</i>

253
00:18:17,479 --> 00:18:19,947
He gave me copies of the letters
which are in a file...

254
00:18:20,149 --> 00:18:24,279
...that I'm putting in your briefcase
with the case file.

255
00:18:24,820 --> 00:18:27,789
There's a drop tomorrow.
I said he should plan...

256
00:18:27,990 --> 00:18:29,457
