it finally stopped raining?

319
00:22:10,946 --> 00:22:14,677
What are you doing over there,
if you don't mind my asking? Level 8?

320
00:22:14,816 --> 00:22:16,010
What?

321
00:22:16,785 --> 00:22:18,946
Are you doing about an 8?

322
00:22:19,354 --> 00:22:20,321
Seven.

323
00:22:20,522 --> 00:22:21,489
Seven.

