340
00:23:33,695 --> 00:23:37,654
One of the best shooting teams.
I know. I went to school in Cambridge.

341
00:23:37,866 --> 00:23:40,391
The Starks are a long dynasty
of Celtic fans.

342
00:23:42,938 --> 00:23:45,270
This is my good friend Gerald Auerbach.

343
00:23:45,974 --> 00:23:47,305
Nick Carmine.

344
00:23:51,146 --> 00:23:53,614
How was everything for you, Mr. Carmine?

345
00:23:53,815 --> 00:23:55,009
Terrific.

346
00:23:55,217 --> 00:23:58,778
Daisy, could I book
