367
00:25:07,055 --> 00:25:08,545
Fantastic.

368
00:25:25,073 --> 00:25:26,973
Wait at the end.

369
00:25:58,006 --> 00:25:59,974
I really hope you're being followed.

370
00:26:00,175 --> 00:26:01,608
You can't be too careful...

371
00:26:02,210 --> 00:26:04,644
...because we need to talk now.

372
00:26:04,846 --> 00:26:06,177
First of all...

373
00:26:07,115 --> 00:26:08,480
...how was your trip?

374
00:26:09,517 --> 00:26:10,745
Fine.

375
00:26:11,453 --> 00:26:12,579
Good.

376
00:26:12,787 --> 00:26:14,914
I just left Stark at the gym.

377
00:26:15,123 --> 00:26:17,591
Some major revelations. Guy's a mess.

378
00:26:17,792 --> 00:26:20,761
Somebody's holding something
serious over his head...

379
00:26:20,962 --> 00:26:22,793
...and I don't think it's about money.

380
00:26:23,531 --> 00:26:26,091
<i>He doesn't move
like a white-collar criminal.</i>

381
00:26:26,301 --> 00:26:28,496
<i>When he walks, his shoulders...</i>

382
00:26:28,703 --> 00:26:30,261
<i>... ride at ear level.</i>

383
00:26:30,472 --> 00:26:34,431
<i>Also, he cut himself shaving
3 times in the last 10 days or so.</i>

384
00:26:34,943 --> 00:26:38,811
These are symptoms
of a deeply ingrained paranoid fear.

385
00:26:39,547 --> 00:26:41,344
Fear of being found out.

386
00:26:41,549 --> 00:26:46,111
<i>I get on the treadmill next to his and I
get my machine going at his exact pace.</i>

387
00:26:46,321 --> 00:26:48,516
<i>I ask him what level he's running at.</i>

388
00:26:48,823 --> 00:26:52,020
<i>I guess 8. He says level 7.</i>

389
00:26:52,227 --> 00:26:54,787
<i>I'm running at the same speed he is.</i>

390
00:26:54,996 --> 00:26:56,395
<i>Level 5.</i>

391
00:26:56,765 --> 00:26:59,029
<i>He'd sooner lie to
a complete stranger...</i>

392
00:26:59,234 --> 00:27:02,397
<i>... than to admit to being
3 levels below my guess.</i>

393
00:27:02,671 --> 00:27:05,299
<i>As soon as I talk to him,
he runs the other way.</i>

394
00:27:05,507 --> 00:27:07,372
<i>It's conditioning, though.
A reflex.</i>

395
00:27:07,575 --> 00:27:11,534
He obviously didn't think to connect me
to the blackmail business at all.

396
00:27:11,780 --> 00:27:13,475
<i>If he'd suspected me...</i>

397
00:27:13,715 --> 00:27:16,548
<i>... he would have remembered my name,
which he didn't.</i>

398
00:27:16,751 --> 00:27:21,313
Also, like most lvy League graduates,
he drops his alma mater with...

399
00:27:21,523 --> 00:27:23,650
...almost no prompting whatsoever.

400
00:27:23,992 --> 00:27:27,018
<i>I say Celtics, he says Cambridge.</i>

401
00:27:27,295 --> 00:27:32,028
<i>Oh yeah, the gentleman prefers redheads.
He lusts after his red-haired masseuse.</i>

402
00:27:32,867 --> 00:27:34,994
<i>You can tell by the way
he takes his massage.</i>

403
00:27:35,203 --> 00:27:37,171
<i>It's more than a little eroticized.</i>

404
00:27:37,472 --> 00:27:40,407
<i>He does it every day at the same time
with the same woman.</i>

405
00:27:40,608 --> 00:27:43,441
<i>I found an e-mail message
from Clearburg.</i>

406
00:27:43,645 --> 00:27:45,340
<i>Kind of cryptic. Note said...</i>

407
00:27:45,547 --> 00:27:49,039
<i>..."Thorough check finds no boxer
